                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the ETHOS LENDING trademark.
                           


Status Update!
                          On Wednesday, June 28, 2017, status on the ETHOS LENDING trademark changed to NON-FINAL OFFICE ACTION ISSUED - CLARIFICATION NEEDED.
                        






On Tuesday, January 21, 2014,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        ETHOS LENDING by 
                        Ethos Lending LLC, San Francisco, CA  94105.
                        The USPTO has given the ETHOS LENDING 
                        trademark serial  number of  86171480.  
